### 🟡 Milestone 4: Authentication

**Mức độ**: ⭐⭐ Trung bình — Laravel có sẵn scaffolding

**Bạn sẽ học**:
- Laravel Breeze — auth scaffolding (login, register, reset password)
- Middleware `auth` — bảo vệ routes
- `Auth` facade — truy cập user hiện tại

**Cài đặt:**
```bash
composer require laravel/breeze --dev
php artisan breeze:install blade

# Breeze tự tạo:
# - Routes: login, register, password reset, email verify
# - Controllers: Auth controllers
# - Views: Blade templates
# - Migration cho password reset tokens

php artisan migrate
npm install && npm run build
```

> [!NOTE]
> Breeze tương đương với việc ta phải tự code `LoginForm`, `SignupForm`, `PasswordResetRequestForm` trong Yii2. Laravel làm hết cho bạn chỉ với 1 lệnh.

---

### 🟡 Milestone 5: Task CRUD + Form Requests

**Mức độ**: ⭐⭐ Trung bình — Core feature

**Bạn sẽ học**:
- Resource Controllers — CRUD tự động
- Form Requests — validation tách riêng (thay vì validate trong model)
- Route Model Binding — tự động inject model
- Authorization Policies

**Cấu trúc file:**
```
app/
├── Http/
│   ├── Controllers/
│   │   └── TaskController.php       (Resource Controller)
│   └── Requests/
│       ├── StoreTaskRequest.php     (= TaskCreateForm trong Yii2)
│       └── UpdateTaskRequest.php    (= TaskUpdateForm trong Yii2)
├── Policies/
│   └── TaskPolicy.php               (Authorization)
```

#### Routes
```php
// routes/web.php
Route::middleware('auth')->group(function () {
    Route::resource('tasks', TaskController::class);
    Route::patch('tasks/{task}/status', [TaskController::class, 'updateStatus'])
         ->name('tasks.update-status');
});
```

#### Form Request (thay thế Yii2 Form Object)
```php
// app/Http/Requests/StoreTaskRequest.php
namespace App\Http\Requests;

use App\Enums\TaskStatus;
use Illuminate\Foundation\Http\FormRequest;
use Illuminate\Validation\Rule;

class StoreTaskRequest extends FormRequest
{
    public function authorize(): bool
    {
        return true; // đã check auth ở middleware
    }

    public function rules(): array
    {
        return [
            'title'       => ['required', 'string', 'max:255'],
            'description' => ['nullable', 'string', 'max:255'],
            'content'     => ['nullable', 'string'],
            'assignee_id' => ['nullable', 'exists:users,id'],
            'due_at'      => ['nullable', 'date', 'after:now'],
            'status'      => ['nullable', Rule::enum(TaskStatus::class)],
        ];
    }
}
```

> [!TIP]
> **So sánh Yii2 vs Laravel**:
> - Yii2: Validation rules ở trong Model → vi phạm SRP
> - Laravel: Validation ở Form Request, tách biệt khỏi Model → tuân thủ SRP
> - Yii2: Route phải khai báo từng action
> - Laravel: `Route::resource()` tạo 7 routes (index, create, store, show, edit, update, destroy) chỉ 1 dòng

---

### 🟡 Milestone 6: Service Layer & Repository Pattern (SOLID)

**Mức độ**: ⭐⭐⭐ Trung bình-Khó — Architecture pattern

**Bạn sẽ học**:
- Service Pattern — business logic tách khỏi controller
- Repository Pattern — data access layer
- Interface binding — Dependency Injection via Service Container
- Service Provider — đăng ký binding

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Đây chính là pattern đã dùng trong Yii2 source (`TaskService`, `TaskRepository`, interfaces). Laravel hỗ trợ DI container mạnh mẽ hơn nhiều.

**Cấu trúc file:**
```
app/
├── Contracts/                        (= Interfaces)
│   ├── TaskServiceInterface.php
│   └── TaskRepositoryInterface.php
├── Services/
│   └── TaskService.php
├── Repositories/
│   └── TaskRepository.php
├── Providers/
│   └── RepositoryServiceProvider.php (Binding interfaces → implementations)
```

#### Interface (Contract)
```php
// app/Contracts/TaskRepositoryInterface.php
namespace App\Contracts;

use App\Models\Task;
use Illuminate\Pagination\LengthAwarePaginator;

interface TaskRepositoryInterface
{
    public function findById(int $id): ?Task;
    public function findByIdForUser(int $taskId, int $userId): ?Task;
    public function search(array $filters): LengthAwarePaginator;
    public function save(Task $task): bool;
    public function delete(Task $task): bool;
}
```

#### Service Provider (DI Container)
```php
// app/Providers/RepositoryServiceProvider.php
namespace App\Providers;

use Illuminate\Support\ServiceProvider;
use App\Contracts\{TaskRepositoryInterface, TaskServiceInterface};
use App\Repositories\TaskRepository;
use App\Services\TaskService;

class RepositoryServiceProvider extends ServiceProvider
{
    public function register(): void
    {
        $this->app->bind(TaskRepositoryInterface::class, TaskRepository::class);
        $this->app->bind(TaskServiceInterface::class, TaskService::class);
    }
}
```

> [!TIP]
> **So sánh Yii2 vs Laravel DI**:
> - Yii2: `$this->repository = $repository ?? new TaskRepository();` — fallback thủ công
> - Laravel: `$this->app->bind(Interface::class, Implementation::class)` — container auto-resolve, swap implementation dễ dàng khi test

