### 🔴 Milestone 10: Queue Jobs & Background Processing

**Mức độ**: ⭐⭐⭐⭐ Khó — Async processing

**Bạn sẽ học**:
- Queue system — dispatch jobs
- Mail notifications
- Scheduled tasks (Task Scheduler)

```bash
php artisan make:job SendTaskNotification
php artisan make:notification TaskAssigned
php artisan queue:work
```

