**Mức độ**: ⭐⭐⭐⭐ Khó — Chất lượng code

**Bạn sẽ học**:
- Feature Tests — test HTTP endpoints
- Unit Tests — test services, models
- Database testing — `RefreshDatabase`, factories
- Mocking — test isolation

```bash
php artisan make:test TaskServiceTest --unit
php artisan make:test TaskControllerTest
php artisan make:factory TaskFactory --model=Task
php artisan test
```

