### 🔴 Milestone 12: CI/CD & Final Polish

**Mức độ**: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Nâng cao

- GitHub Actions CI pipeline
- Caching (Redis)
- Rate limiting cho API
- Logging & error handling
- Documentation (API docs)

